Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A spinning seed landed on a tiny rabbit's\Nnose and pointed toward adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the autumn orchard, the rabbit learned that\Na tiny bird had lost the nest it called home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What began as a rescue mission grew harder\Nwhen the leaf map slipped out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The thoughtful rabbit decided to reach the stranded friend\Nand asked nearby animals to form a cheerful helping line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan worked, bringing a safe rescue\Nfor everyone in the autumn orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The final puddle ripple formed a heart before fading away.\NThe leaf map softly echoed the adventure's beginning.
